  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior IT Specialist",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a skilled <strong>Senior IT Specialist</strong> to lead system integration, cloud infrastructure management, and internal IT operations. You will work closely with sales, product, and client teams to design solutions, troubleshoot technical issues, and ensure smooth, secure, and scalable IT environments.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Lead system integration efforts and support outsourcing partners.</li><li>Work with sales team to define and prototype product specifications.</li><li>Develop reliable applications based on client needs.</li><li>Serve as the main technical contact for clients; diagnose and resolve issues with minimal downtime.</li><li>Manage and optimize cloud infrastructure, security, costs, and regional deployments.</li><li>Provide technical expertise and consultation to internal teams and clients.</li><li>Maintain documentation and architectural diagrams.</li><li>Support internal IT operations to ensure efficient day‑to‑day performance.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Degree in IT, Computer Science, or related field.</li><li>5+ years of experience in IT infrastructure, cloud technologies, or systems engineering.</li><li>Strong knowledge of AWS/Azure/Google Cloud.</li><li>Excellent troubleshooting and communication skills.</li><li>Relevant certifications (AWS, Azure, CCNA, ITIL) are advantageous.</li></ul>",
