    "description": "<p>\r\n\tIncorporated in 1978 and based in Singapore, Hitachi Aqua-Tech Engineering Pte. Ltd. stands out in the water treatment industry by offering full EPC capabilities across a wide range of projects. With a strong focus on reverse osmosis (RO) and demineralization systems, we are a complete system builder equipped with comprehensive engineering capabilities and in-house manufacturing facilities.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\tHitachi Aqua-Tech water treatment systems are installed globally in various industries ranging from food processing, health care, cogeneration plants, electronics, marine, military, FPSO, aviation, to hotels and resorts.</div>\r\n",
